sources.title: Goketsu Jiraiya (Jiraiya the Hero) [1921]
sources.description: Goketsu Jiraiya (Jiraiya the Hero) is a Japanese silent film from 1921. Runtime (this version) : 20 minutes 48 seconds Director : Shozo Makino Cast : Matsunosuke Onoe as Jiraiya, Suminojo Ichikawa as Orochimaru, Kijaku Otani as Tsukikagegunryo Miyukinosuke, Chosei Kataoka as Tsunatehime, Shoen Kataoka as Takasago Yuminosuke, Enichiro Jitsukawa, Ichitaro Kataoka, Masatada Makino.
